title: Week 11 preview & Bills vs. Dolphins recap
itunes:title: Week 11 preview & Bills vs. Dolphins recap
description:
A room with some heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- preview every Week 11 game on the NFL schedule and recap "Thursday Night Football" between the Bills and Dolphins.
